pygtk: pygtk (GTK+2 Bindings for Python)
pygtk:
pygtk: PyGTK lets you easily create applications with a graphical user
pygtk: interface using the Python programming language. PyGTK uses the GTK+
pygtk: toolkit to offer a comprehensive set of graphical elements and other
pygtk: useful programming facilities, like the handling of internationalized
pygtk: text (bidirectional text or non-latin gliph sets), first class                                                                         
pygtk: accesibility support through the Gnome Accessibility Framework (ATK                                                                    
pygtk: library).                                                                                                                              
